name: LELE KOMBO
description:
Game recehan Alenka Inventra lagi nyusun mesin dari pesawat. Ada beberapa game mode, kebuka kalau udah selesai dari sebelumnya. Yang pernah main Bishi Bashi pasti kenal~

A quick game about Alenka Inventra making machines out of planes. There's several game modes, unlockable once you finish the previous ones. If you play Bishi Bashi, this should be familiar~

Fangame buat Vtuber Digikagi: Alenka Inventra
Congrats on 100k subs!
